              "content": "Learn and practice lettering techniques to create meaningful and inspirational hand-lettered art. Lesson topics include serifed, sans-serifed, and script fonts, line width and value, guidelines, outlines, and shadow lines, key principles of design, dimension, and shading. Each term concludes with a project, and skills can be used to create beautiful collections of mottoes and quotes in a Commonplace Book or for display or gifts."
